DOC.brief_summary: To evaluate long-term safety of YVOIRE classic s by incidence of adverse events including injection site local reactions and biodegradability
DOC.brief_title: Observational Study to Evaluate Long-term Safety and Biodegradability of YVOIRE Classic s
DOC.criteria: Age is over 18 years old Must be willing and able to provide written informed consent Sensitive to hyaluronic acid or any excipients of study product Have history of streptococcal disease, severe allergy or anaphylaxis or bleeding disorders. Women in pregnancy or lactation
